Men's Bantamweight - Weightlifting - Rio 2016 Summer Olympics

Men's Bantamweight - Weightlifting - Sydney 2000 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     Athletes competed in two types of lift: the snatch, in which they raised the bar over the head in one movement, and the clean & jerk, in which they raised the bar i two movements using the combined strength of arms and legs.
